snippet.title: Longplay of Namco Museum 50th Anniversary
snippet.description:
Longplay of Namco Museum 50th Anniversary, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Aug. 30th, 2005. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:24 - Pac-Man
01:54 - Ms. Pac-Man
03:05 - Mappy
04:51 - Galaxian
07:06 - Galaga
08:33 - Dragon Spirit
09:44 - Dig Dug
10:46 - Bosconian
12:00 - Pac-Mania (20,000 points in Ms. Pacman & 15,000 in Pac-Man)
13:41 - Galaga '88 (40,000 points in Galaga)
15:20 - Xevious
16:45 - Sky Kid
17:55 - Rolling Thunder
19:11 - Rally-X
20:25 - Pole Position II
22:36 - Pole Position
24:29 - Credits
